Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:42.16,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}感情的烈马 一旦任之脱缰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.32,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}便再也找不到方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:53.71,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}罪恶的扳机 本已沾染血光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.00,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}却渐渐辨不清形状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.80,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}若要将恨意驱赶出心房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.39,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}还如何让你把命偿?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.27,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘尘封过往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:20.40,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只为填罪业汪洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.62,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}怨凛冽锋芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:32.29,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}颔首抚刻骨心伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:40.42,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}苦痛亦尽数遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.97,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}身陷曲折回廊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:51.89,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}既迷失原本模样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.44,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}何不遁世韬光?
